Building this project is quite simple.

Debug release:
    cd src/Debug/
    make

Non-Debug release
    cd src/Release
    make
    
We haven't make a configure file yet. 
Dependencies: 
libbluez (>=3.09): http://www.bluez.org/
libmxml: http://mxml.sourceforge.net/
libcurl: http://curl.haxx.se/download.html



